metadata.name: Little Corn & Pink bear's Metaverse #1
metadata.description: The first ARU's NFT airdrop painting is also ARU's first work connecting with her baby girl - "Little Corn" ! "Little Corn" is a nickname for ARU's baby , this painting is a gift that want to thanks her baby to choose ARU as a mother. ARU presents the  pink bear in the original way of fluorescent acrylic paint, so that the happiness and warmth of childhood can be more directly revealed.
